---
title: Lamb Bolognese Risotto with Carrot and Parsley
description: Chef Mimi has performed culinary magic with this recipe. She’s combined the best of everyone’s favourite dishes, bolognese and risotto, and the result is the delicious, rich base of bolognese and the creamy consistency of risotto.
